      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Sahl Bin Ziyad, from Ali Bin Asbaat, from Zareeh Al Muharby, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The best of the assistance is the world, upon (seeking) the Herefater’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "15. A number of our people have narrated from Sahl ibn Ziyad from Ali ibn Asbat from Darih al-Muharibiy who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘The worldly help in one’s quest for success in the hereafter is the best help.’” "
        ]
      }
